*****************RUNNING A NETLIST FILE and VIEWING THE SIMULATION RESULTS*************************
STEP1:- enter the directory in which the netlist file is saved

STEP2:- enter the command to run the netlist file
     ************************************
     *   ngspice netlistfilename.net    *
     ************************************

This opens the ngspice prompt.
If you dont want the prompt to appear then enter the command
     ************************************
     *  ngspice -b netlistfilename.net  *
     ************************************

STEP3:- After running the netlist file.The data is stored in a .dat file.

STEP4:- The obtained datafile is imported in python. And then results are plotted.

